doc.ContractDescription: IGF::OT::IGF ENVIRONMENTAL ASSESSMENT FOR MILCON P-758 MACHINERY CONTROL DEVELOPMENT CENTER THE PURPOSE OF THIS TASK ORDER MODIFICATION IS TO SHIFT EFFORT UNDER ORIGINAL TASKS 2, 3, 4, AND 5 FROM SUPPORTING AN ENVIRONMENTAL ASSESSMENT (EA) FOR MILCON P-758 AT NSA MECHANICSBURG TO AN EFFORT TO COMPLETE ASSOCIATED ENVIRONMENTAL STUDIES IN SUPPORT OF FUTURE NATIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL POLICY ACT (NEPA) WORK. EFFORT FOR TASKS 2, 3, 4, AND 5 SHALL BE DELETED PERTAINING TO THE EA AND REPLACED WITH EFFORT TO SUPPORT ASSOCIATED ENVIRONMENTAL STUDIES TO COMPLETE FUTURE NEPA WORK AS DETAILED BELOW UNDER REVISED TASK 2. OPTIONAL TASKS 6 AND 7 SHALL ALSO BE DELETED FROM THIS SOW. THE EA IS NO LONGER NEEDED DUE TO VERY RECENT CHANGES IN NAVY ENVIRONMENTAL POLICY THAT NOW ALLOWS THE PROJECT TO BE COMPLETED UNDER A CATEGORICAL EXCLUSION INSTEAD OF AN EA WITH REGARD TO ANALYZING ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACTS OF THE PROJECT.
